{"tid":766324,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"依個洋腸, 你做得太多","createTime":"2018-08-03T13:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T16:45:33.000Z","uid":187153,"like":26,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6726021118e7cdb630f2ff998571acd03695b433","tid":766324,"uid":187153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"原本無諗出POST, 但係依個洋腸又打電話, 又Send野俾我個friend, 依個洋腸關心既人已經太多, 連人地個老母都搵?!<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可幫下佢, 佢話港女性感叫床聲夠大, 想話香港人食屎, 佢仲想博士畢業後留係香港, 希望大家幫下佢, 等佢可以繼續留係香港生活.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/213056_e49e7a08388c6d5e3bdff89ef2ba69f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F213056_e49e7a08388c6d5e3bdff89ef2ba69f1.jpg&h=6838935a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次唔好咁易俾人試倒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/213110_8357f6de27335f94d77a096a2cfb2d60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F213110_8357f6de27335f94d77a096a2cfb2d60.jpg&h=ba4fef5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女: 好難想像搵西人做男朋友, 點解你搵一個香港(女)<br />\n<br />\n西人: 點解? 好多西人對華裔女仔有興趣<br />\n<br />\n女: 佢地諗華裔女仔係好啲?<br />\n<br />\n西人: 佢地諗華裔女仔係性感, 做愛果時叫床聲夠大&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女: 噢, 你係咪有好多華裔女? 叫床聲夠大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n西人: 我約過幾個, 有10個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女: 佢地有無上你屋企<br />\n<br />\n西人: 有時酒店<br />\n<br />\n女: 我好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/213230_337fe629882fc4c98187ab12c6fe5386.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F213230_337fe629882fc4c98187ab12c6fe5386.jpg&h=0f0b90f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有女朋友, 又一而再約人, 關心人. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/213344_d089b5a4677d881a36535143ab8b75da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F213344_d089b5a4677d881a36535143ab8b75da.jpg&h=4d6f595d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢好憎香港人, 但係又成日約港女, 好想留係香港, 唔知咩原因. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/213802_77a8cbcffdabe2a2e88006702310a23d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F213802_77a8cbcffdabe2a2e88006702310a23d.jpg&h=bfcf048c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫下佢, 等佢個學生驗證過期之前搵倒份好工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可以留係香港, 唔好再搵第二個."},{"pid":"b54ccd4a6442d03dfffe3004c393e4bc4472c3f1","tid":766324,"uid":5652,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:42:50.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"ada5f1468306ff837091177bc188597ff90b704a","tid":766324,"uid":67655,"like":47,"dislike":4,"score":43,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"你係唔鍾意個鬼佬<br />\n就直接屌佢啦<br />\n係到互flirt<br />\n唔怪得鬼佬以為港女easy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386909278f994bd745659ccc798f69c16c12107e","tid":766324,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:49:22.000Z","msg":"泰仔黎？"},{"pid":"80a00a1e7e0a9cdd04dcf07bd8bb87745aaacf69","tid":766324,"uid":104965,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6726021118e7cdb630f2ff998571acd03695b433","tid":766324,"uid":187153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"原本無諗出POST, 但係依個洋腸又打電話, 又Send野俾我個friend, 依個洋腸關心既人已經太多, 連人地個老母都搵?!<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可幫下佢, 佢話港女性感叫床聲夠大, 想話香港人食屎, 佢仲想博士畢業後留係香港, 希望大家幫下佢, 等佢